titleStmt.title: Vǫluspá (Hauksbók version) : AM 544 4to : A digital edition

availability.p: Licence accepted by the editor Karl G. Johansson in a mail to Odd Einar Haugen 2 November 2015.

projectDesc.p: This manuscript text has been encoded according to the standard set out in The Menota handbook (version 2.0 beta), at http://www.menota.org/guidelines as of 2007-01-30.

correction.p: This text has been proofread by Karl G. Johansson, University of Oslo.

normalization.p: This text has been encoded on two levels: facsimile and diplomatic.

interpretation.p: This text has not been lemmatised or morphologically analysed.
